If you have any problem when using this skill, you can contact us by email: support@yg-ai.com

Smart Device skill for Amazon Alexa to help you easily control your devices.
You can just ask Alexa to turn on, off.
No need to manually control your device - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, or Echo Show.
Connect Alexa and your smart devices by following steps:
(1). Download your smart device app from the Android or iOS app market;
(2). Registered and login your smart device app account;
(3). You need to have smart devices on hand;
(4). Configure these devices in your smart device app and set your devices nickname (easy to identify);
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with the "Alexa" app;
(7). Look for the skill "Smart Device" in the skill categories of "Alexa";
(8). Click on the "Enable" button of the "Smart Device" skill to access the login page for your smart device application;
(9). Choose your smart device app and Input your smart device app account and password, "log in",you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all the setup is done.
You can enjoy voice control on your home devices such as:
"Alexa, discover devices."
"Alexa, turn on the robot."
"Alexa, turn off the robot."
